{"id":"latchet","term":"Latchet","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A thong (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 22:25\">Acts 22:25</a>), cord, or strap fastening the sandal on the foot (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 5:27\">Isa. 5:27</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Mark 1:7\">Mark 1:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 3:16\">Luke 3:16</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Acts 22:25","Isaiah 5:27","Mark 1:7","Luke 3:16"]}